data.description: Charming and inviting, you'll love the spacious covered front porch on this single level home in the popular Northridge subdivision in Prineville! Enter into an airy and comfortable living space with vaulted ceilings, efficient kitchen and dining area with sliders leading to the back patio. The bedrooms are nicely sized and the primary bedroom comfortably fits a king size bed as well as offers a spacious walk in closet. The current owners have done some great updates in the past year including a brand new roof, solar panels, beautiful waterproof flooring throughout the home, quartz kitchen countertops, new smart oven (doubles as an airfryer!) and microwave, a bathroom refresh with new toilets, as well as a pergola and hot tub added to the large back patio. This home also offers RV or boat parking with a newly constructed gate for access between the RV area and fully fenced back yard. You won't want to miss this one!
